"``route_id`` / ``route_name`` / ``events_count`` / ``unique_products`` / "
"``total_amount`` / ``total_gold`` / ``ticks_span`` / ``tons_per_min`` / "
"``gold_per_min``"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.routes.rank_routes:10 of
