"``ticks_span`` は events の min/max timestamp_tick の差． ``tons_per_min`` / "
"``gold_per_min`` は正規化 (分換算)．"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/api/analysis.rst:34
msgid "Persistence (chronic / transient)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence:1 of
msgid "慢性 vs 一過性の deficit 分類．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence:3 of
msgid ""
"StorageTrends の 120 点時系列を舐めて，在庫 0 (= 欠品) の頻度から ``chronic`` / "
"``transient`` / ``stable`` を判定．書記長の Decision Matrix (#88) の入力になる．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence.classify_deficit:1 of
msgid "島 × 物資の deficit 持続性分類．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence.classify_deficit:6 of
msgid ""
"``island_name`` / ``product_guid`` / ``stockout_ratio`` / ``latest`` / "
"``peak`` / ``mean`` / ``slope`` / ``category``"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence.classify_deficit:9 of
msgid "``stockout_ratio`` = samples 中の値 0 の割合．1.0 に近いほど慢性． ``category``:"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence.classify_deficit:11 of
msgid "``chronic``  : ratio >= 0.50"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence.classify_deficit:12 of
msgid "``transient``: 0.10 <= ratio < 0.50"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.persistence.classify_deficit:13 of
msgid "``stable``   : < 0.10 (実質欠品なし)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/api/analysis.rst:40
msgid "Sensitivity (leave-one-out)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity:1 of
msgid "「船 1 隻減らす」感度分析 (leave-one-out)．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity:3 of
msgid ""
"書記長「船1隻減らすならどこ？」．TradeEvent ledger から各 route の 輸送寄与を集計し，1 route "
"ずつ除外した時に影響を受ける島を特定する． 簡易 MVP: TradeEvent の route 別 volume を現 balance "
"から「差し引いた」 仮想 delta で deficit 増加数を数える．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity.route_leave_one_out:1 of
msgid "各 route を除外した時の「追加 deficit 物資数」．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity.route_leave_one_out:6 of
msgid ""
"``route_id`` / ``route_name`` / ``tons_per_min`` / ``affected_products`` "
"/ ``added_deficit_count`` / ``recommended_action``"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity.route_leave_one_out:9 of
msgid "仮定:"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity.route_leave_one_out:10 of
msgid ""
"route の輸送量 ``tons_per_min`` は history から推定．route 除外は 「到着島で ``consumed`` "
"が発生しなくなる = delta に + 加算」と近似． (実体は生産地側の余剰で補填されるので双方影響だが MVP は消費地側のみ)．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity.route_leave_one_out:14 of
msgid "``recommended_action``:"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity.route_leave_one_out:15 of
msgid "``safe_to_remove``: added_deficit_count == 0"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity.route_leave_one_out:16 of
msgid "``impacts_<N>_products``: N > 0"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.sensitivity.route_leave_one_out:18 of
msgid "rows=0 の場合 (events 無し) は空 DataFrame．"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/api/analysis.rst:46
msgid "Forecast"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast:1 of
msgid "人口成長 / 消費 予測．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast:3 of
msgid "Logistic Growth (S-curve) は時系列データが要るが現 save は単一 snapshot なので MVP では:"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast:6 of
msgid ""
"``consumption_forecast``: 現 delta_per_minute が N 時間続いたら累積 不足量はいくら? "
"の線形投影．短期 (24h 以内) には妥当．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast:8 of
msgid ""
"``population_capacity_proxy``: ``full_house`` と ``residence_count`` から "
"「あと何人入れられるか」の空き capacity を簡単に出す．logistic の ``carrying_capacity`` 代替．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast:12 of
msgid "時系列 logistic fit は別 issue で複数 snapshot を読み込む機構ができた後．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast.consumption_forecast:1 of
msgid "現状の delta が ``hours_ahead`` 時間持続した場合の累積不足量．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast.consumption_forecast:3 of
msgid ""
"``delta_per_minute`` × ``minutes`` で単純線形投影．``projected_delta_total`` が負 ="
" その物資はその時間で赤字累積．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast.population_capacity_proxy:1 of
msgid "住居あたり最大人数から「空き capacity」を推定．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.forecast.population_capacity_proxy:3 of
msgid ""
"``per_house=10`` は Farmer の ``fullHouse``．実際は tier ごとに違うので tier breakdown"
" が必要だが MVP は均等 proxy．正確版は後続 PR．"
msgstr ""

