#: ../../source/api/analysis.rst:58
msgid "Min-Cost Flow allocation"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:1 of
msgid "需給ギャップの最適割当 (v0.5-I #89)．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:3 of
msgid ""
"供給余剰島 → 赤字島への物資分配を ``networkx.max_flow_min_cost`` で解く． 全 demand を満たせない場合は"
" partial flow を返す．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:6 of
msgid "## Graph 構造 (物資ごと)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:8 of
msgid "``` SRC → supplier_1 (cap=excess_1) ──┐"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:10 of
msgid "├─→ demander_1 (cap=need_1) → SNK"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:11 of
msgid "SRC → supplier_2 (cap=excess_2) ──┤                                ↑"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:12 of
msgid "└─→ demander_2 (cap=need_2) ────┘"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:13 of
msgid "```"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:15 of
msgid "``SRC → supplier`` の cap = 供給余剰"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:16 of
msgid "``demander → SNK`` の cap = 不足量"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:17 of
msgid "``supplier → demander`` は無限 cap，cost は距離 proxy"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:19 of
msgid "## 距離 proxy"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation:21 of
msgid ""
"``session_by_area_manager`` が渡されれば session 一致で cost=1，不一致で cost=10．未指定なら全"
" edge cost=1 (距離区別なし)．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation.optimal_flow:1 of
msgid "各物資の供給余剰→赤字 flow を min-cost で解く．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation.optimal_flow:3 of
msgid ""
"``balance_df`` は ``analysis.frames.to_frames(state).balance`` の形式を "
"想定．``delta_per_minute > 0`` = 供給余剰，``< 0`` = 赤字として扱う．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.allocation.optimal_flow:6 of
msgid "戻り値: 1 row = 1 (product, source, sink) 割当．flow=0 の組は省略．"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/api/analysis.rst:64
msgid "OR-Tools VRP"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:1 of
msgid "VRP (Vehicle Routing Problem) 最適化 — v0.5 最終本丸 (#13)．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:3 of
msgid ""
"OR-Tools ``RoutingModel`` を使って **物資ごとの pickup-and-delivery VRP** を解く．船数 +"
" capacity + 距離 heuristic の制約で各 vehicle の経路を 決定し，Min-Cost Flow "
"より現実的な「船何隻でどう回るか」の計画を返す．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:7 of
msgid "## 設計"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:9 of
msgid "各物資を独立に解く (物資間の船共有はしない MVP)．理由:"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:11 of
msgid "Anno では物資種別ごとに船が区別されることが多い (Schooner が食料， Clipper が工業品など)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:13 of
msgid "物資混載は save から取れない情報 (ship のカーゴ構成は内部保存されず)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:14 of
msgid "物資独立にすれば各 product の VRP は小規模で OR-Tools が即解ける"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:16 of
msgid "各物資について:"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:18 of
msgid "depot (仮想) + supplier ノード + demander ノードを持つ graph"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:19 of
msgid ""
"supplier は「pickup」，demander は「delivery」．RoutingModel の "
"pickups_and_deliveries 制約で pair 化"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:21 of
msgid "距離 matrix は session_by_area_manager (同 session=1 / 別=10)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:22 of
msgid "各 vehicle のカーゴ capacity 制約 + 船数制約"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:24 of
msgid "## 出力"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:26 of
msgid "``routes``: 解けた vehicle 経路のリスト (空 route は除外)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:27 of
msgid "``unmet_demand``: capacity / 船数不足で割当られなかった需要"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:28 of
msgid "``objective_value``: 総距離 (コスト和)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize:29 of
msgid "``solve_status``: OR-Tools の solution status"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize.OptimizedStop:1 of
msgid "1 経路 1 stop．pickup か delivery を区別．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize.OptimizedRoute:1 of
msgid "1 vehicle が回る経路．``stops`` は訪問順．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize.UnmetDemand:1 of
msgid "解けなかった需要．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize.OptimizedPlan:1 of
msgid "VRP 全体の解．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize.optimize_routes:1 of
msgid "物資ごとに PDP-VRP を解いて輸送計画を返す．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.analysis.optimize.optimize_routes:3 of
msgid ""
"``vehicle_capacity`` は 1 trip で運べる tons (scaled 値ではなく人間に わかりやすい tons "
"単位)．``time_limit_seconds`` は各物資の solve 時間上限．"
msgstr ""

